    "PSTs enrolled in the primary specialization were required to complete two core mathematics curriculum and pedagogy courses as part of their degree program.",
    "One of these courses emphasized the use of problem-solving strategies in teaching mathematics.",
    "In this course assignment, PSTs were tasked with solving various mathematical problems using multiple strategies within the primary school context.",
    "For this study, a single mathematical problem was selected from the primary school mathematics curriculum.",
    "Participants were instructed to use strategies relevant to the content and children's context, particularly for upper primary year levels (age nine-age 11)."
